            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1639392241780-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, stir the<strong> roasted veg </strong>through the pasta and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>baked ratatouille & chicken tortiglioni</strong></p><p>Tear your<strong> basil leaves </strong>over the top and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
